snippet.textDisplay: I am a pakistani and this song has been sing amazingly but singers should have taken care of pronunciations. It's "Qadam" not "Kadam". In normal conversation such things can be ignored but when it comes to singing one needs to take care of these intricacies. In this case our singers should learn from indian singers like ata Mangeshkar, Asha Bhosle, Kishore Kumar etc who took care of their pronunciations and specially learned Urdu tp get their diction right
